# CAPSTONE-1

A modern, responsive website built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This capstone project demonstrates front-end web development skills with a multi-page layout featuring home, about, services, blog, and contact sections.

##  Project Overview

CAPSTONE-1 is a professional website template showcasing essential web development techniques. The project combines semantic HTML structure, responsive CSS styling, and interactive JavaScript functionality to create an engaging user experience across all devices.

